I18N_SPLASH_FIRST_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTIO: Timsirin n Oppia, yettawssnen daɣen s yisem n yisniram, ttmuddun-d tirmitin timyigawanin ifazen ugar n tvidyutin neɣ iḍrisen, akken ad mudden tallelt i yiseqdacen ad issinen yis-sen.
I18N_SPLASH_JAVASCRIPT_ERROR_DESCRIPTION: Oppia d asmel ilelli n uɣbalu yeldin n yirmad imyigawnanen ittusemman 'isniram'. Acu kan, Oppia yesra JavaScript ad yettwarmed ɣef yiminig-ik web akken ad yeddu akken iwata, ihi ɣef yiminig-ik yensa. Ma tesriḍ tallelt akken ad tremdeḍ JavaScript, sit da.
I18N_SPLASH_SECOND_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTI: Isniram fessusit i tmerna. Ttawin abrid n tektiwin i d-ttmuddun yimdanen rnan tteddun akken tella termit n yinelmaden-ik deg umaḍal.
I18N_SPLASH_SUBTITLE: Oppia yessifses timerna n temsirin timyigawanin i yesselmaden, i ileddin allen.
I18N_SPLASH_THIRD_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTIO: Oppia ad k•kem-yeǧǧ ad ternuḍ diɣ ad tebḍuḍ isniram n ddeqs n yisental, ala axemmem-ik•im kan ara yilin d talast.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_COMMUNITY_GUIDELINES_GUI: Yal yiwen ansuf yis-s akken ad yeɛreḍ diɣ ad d-imudd tikti-s ɣef yisniram i d-yeffɣen. S ufus-nwen meṛṛa, Ad nizmir ad nesnerni s war aneḥbus, timsirin ɣef usmel sakin ad tent-nerr lhan ugar akken nezmer.
Seqdec tamuɣli yelhan ticki tessuffuɣeḍ-d isniram. Isniram yessefk ad sɛun azal n usegmi ibanen diɣ ur yessefk ara ad yegber adellel, ispamen, aḥwaṣ neɣ asexṣer.

Ili d aɣerman yelhan. Timerna n ddeqs n yimiḍanen, aseqdec s waṭas n unagraw n tektiwin, aseqdec n yisniram akken ad tkelxeḍ iseqdacen, neɣ yal tikli am ti ur tettwaqbal ara da diɣ ad yeglu s useḥbes n umiḍan-ik.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_COMMUNITY_GUIDELINES_TEX: Ma tebɣiḍ asegzi ɣef tinaḍin-a, suter deg unmager-nneɣ.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_HEADING: Mudd afus i yinelmaden n umaḍal
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_PUBLICATION_INSTRUCTIONS: Selmed taɣawsa yelhan — Mudd-d talɣut tamaynut i yimsefliden isaḍasen — ur sekyad ara kan tamussni i ẓran yakan. Daɣen, ma tebɣiḍ ad teslemdeḍ asentel anida yella yakan usnirem, xemmem ad ternuḍ awennit ɣef usnirem amiran, akken ad tmuddeḍ afus deg usnerni-s — fessus!

Aselmed mačči d aḥekku — Ma tferneḍ isental, ɛreḍ ad tferneḍ, ad tawiḍ tikti iweɛren yesɛan ddeqs n yinumak neɣ lqayet nezzeh, neɣ tagrumma n yisental yemcubaken aṭas. Yezmer daɣen yelha limer ad tesɛuḍ tikti n unerni neɣ acqirrew, akken aselmad ad yesɛu tagnit ad yesnes tikti i yelmed yakan ɣef yiwet n lḥala tamaynut.

Mudd tikti ibennun — Ur qqar ara kan i unelmad dakken yufa-tt-id neɣ yeɣleḍ. Segzi-as amek ara ixemmem, neɣ ddu s telqayt akken ad tɛerḍeḍ ad gzun tuccḍiwin. Seqdec ismektiyen neɣ mudd iwellihen i yisteqsiyen yeldin, diɣ mudd i yinelmaden tiktiwin timaynutin ilaqen.
Ales taɣuri — Ḍmen dakken asnirem-ik yura akken iwata, fessus i tɣuri. Yessefk ad yili s war tuccḍiwin n tira neɣ ibugen, ma ulac ad yesruḥ taflest deg yinelmaden.

Mudd-itt-id s tseddi — Iswi n uselmed ad yettwabgen i yinelmaden yettnadin isniram, diɣ yessefk ad d-imudd udem n ugbur n usnirem-ik. Asnirem yessefk ad d-imudd akk agbur n umiru yellan deg yiswi n uselmed akked usnirem iman-is.

Qqim d imseknu! — Isniram ifazen ḥekkun-d taqsiḍt, ttaran-d tikti ilaqen. Ttmuddun i yinelmaden tignatin n uxemmem ɣef yimegziyen, aɛraḍ n tmussniwin timaynutin, d urmas n tektiwin ilaqen ɣef umahil-nsen.
Ticki yeffeɣ-d usnirem, ad ak-ittunefk, diɣ ad yili yewjed i yal yiwen yebɣan ad yelmed seg-s akken ad d-yesnulfu tarmit ifazen i yinelmaden, ha-tent-a kra  n texbula i nufa lhant!:
Ugar n tallelt ɣef tmerna n tekti yelhan akked tisniram ifazen, wali asebter-nneɣ deg Design Tips.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_PUBLICATION_POLICY_PARAG: Yal ameskar n usnirem uslig ad yizmir ad tt-id-yessuffeɣ melmi yebɣa. Acu kan, isniram n yir taɣara, inedbalen zemren ad tent-ḥebsen, sakin ad d-mudden ayen ilaqen akken ad nnernint.

Isniram ttwafeṣṣlen akken ad ttnernin, wid ur nettwabeddel ara ddeqs n wakud zmren ad ttwaḥesben d "igujilen". Ihi, zemren ad beddlentbab akken ad uɣalen n tmezdagnut Oppia (akken i aɣ-d-iwelleh unedbal), akken ad yizmir ad innerni.
